strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSBLESSING_KEYWOR: <style=cKeywordName><color=#00BDFF>Atuykarounkami's Blessing</color></style><style=cSub>On impact, spawn a <style=cIsDamage>tidal blast</style> after a delay. <style=cIsHealing>Heals</style> for a small amount.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_TWINSSHOCK_KEYWORD: <style=cKeywordName><color=#000FFF>Shocking</color></style><style=cSub>Interrupts enemies and stuns them. The stun is removed if the target takes more than <style=cIsHealth>10%</style> of their maximum health in damage.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PASSIVE_NAME: Ever Turning, Ever Swaying, Ever Drifting
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PASSIVE_DESCRIPTION: Ururuu and Saraana have independent loadouts and <style=cIsUtility>switch turns</style> upon reaching maximum <color=#EDA717>Zeal</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY0_DESCRIPTION: Fire a dark sphere that explodes on impact for <style=cIsDamage>290% damage</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Hold up to 4</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY1_DESCRIPTION: Repeatedly fire <style=cIsUtility>homing</style> bolts for <style=cIsDamage>100% damage</style>. Continous fire will charge a dark sphere that can be released for <style=cIsDamage>600% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_PRIMARY2_DESCRIPTION: Collapse the space around a target for <style=cIsDamage>310% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY1_DESCRIPTI: <style=cIsDamage>Stunning</style>. Fire a boulder for <style=cIsDamage>600% damage</style> that splinters into smaller debris on impact for <style=cIsDamage>5x200% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY0_DESCRIPTI: <style=cIsDamage>Ignite.</style> Conjure a slow-moving molten ball that burns nearby enemies for <style=cIsDamage>100%-200% damage</style> and sets them <style=cIsHealth>alight</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY2_DESCRIPTI: Fire a returning wind blade that repeatedly strikes enemies for <style=cIsDamage>140% damage</style>. Charge to increase distance.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SECONDARY3_DESCRIPTI: Instantly <style=cIsUtility>freeze</style> a single enemy for <style=cIsDamage>100% damage</style> or charge to freeze multiple enemies for <style=cIsDamage>165% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY0_DESCRIPTION: Strike an enemy for <style=cIsDamage>1000% damage</style>. Summons 3 <color=#1661D4>aftershocks</color> for <style=cIsDamage>500% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY1_DESCRIPTION: Fire a series of water bolts for <style=cIsDamage>???% damage</style> each. The number of bolts fired increases with attack speed. Every 3rd bolt has <color=#00BDFF>Atuykarounkami's Blessing</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_UTILITY2_DESCRIPTION: Send a tiriryarai call to Jachdwalt. His afterimages strike enemies for <style=cIsDamage>?x???% damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SPECIAL0_DESCRIPTION: Channel a great roar of darkness for <style=cIsDamage>9800%</style> total <style=cIsDamage>damage</style>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SPECIAL1_DESCRIPTION: Mark an area to be sealed after <style=cIsUtility>2.5 seconds</style>. Once primed, the seal detonates for <style=cIsDamage>650% damage</style>. Enemies below <style=cIsHealth>20% health are executed.</style>
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_SPECIAL2_DESCRIPTION: Manifest the power of an umbral sun, <style=cIsDamage>poisoning</style> enemies each tick with <color=#5D00FF>void fog</color>.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA1_DESCRIPTION: Dissappear into the aether and <style=cIsUtility>become invulnerable</style> but unable to attack.
strings.NINES_KAMUNAGI_BODY_EXTRA4_DESCRIPTION: Call forth Mothmoth to buff your allies with <style=cIsHealth>lifesteal</style>.
